s dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/oceanoinfinito/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cad0b959cf00fc0b4802fe770abed6c2a5e108277c0e4b5fdfb26c3530ef7f7a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cad0b959cf00fc0b4802fe770abed6c2a5e108277c0e4b5fdfb26c3530ef7f7a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/oceanoinfinito/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">oceanoinfinito</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 4, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Elementor  proprio alla portata di tutti, molto semplice, completo e professionale. Lo consiglio a tutti!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fast and easy</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/leilina73/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2d144b88c056be7473869b8aa323bfc763f896eee7dfb30320db6fab2e83fe5b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2d144b88c056be7473869b8aa323bfc763f896eee7dfb30320db6fab2e83fe5b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/leilina73/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">leilina73</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 4, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>easy and simple to use</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Seriously Simple, Seriously Powerful</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zestyvivica/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dc8c9fcc0585ab313516cbff3fea0e641061b9e557f98a8eaf85d601f06051a6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dc8c9fcc0585ab313516cbff3fea0e641061b9e557f98a8eaf85d601f06051a6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zestyvivica/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">zestyvivica</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 28, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Honestly, Elementor has empowered me to finally create the website I\'ve always envisioned. It\'s user-friendly for beginners but still packs a serious punch for more experienced users. If you\'re looking for a website builder that\'s powerful, flexible, and actually enjoyable to use, look no further. Five stars all the way  its worth every penny and then some!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Elementor is very good!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/don-kong/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/accb5a4f2240af9d66442d1977bf8903f8735e6e4d4725a7e7afd47af698a271?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/accb5a4f2240af9d66442d1977bf8903f8735e6e4d4725a7e7afd47af698a271?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/don-kong/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Don Kong</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 28, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Despite some weaknesses, Elementor is very good for creating websites.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Incrvel!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thiesco/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5b0972816fd53c39e84abdc78b925cdf364baee8a47591aba14de5bd8058f993?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5b0972816fd53c39e84abdc78b925cdf364baee8a47591aba14de5bd8058f993?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thiesco/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">thiesco</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 26, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>tima ferramenta!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Stupid customer support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/uckydogie/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a1195d32426d76da899d45df9b9f12f7ef209e62c6c1d8610c21f68bcc76eed3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a1195d32426d76da899d45df9b9f12f7ef209e62c6c1d8610c21f68bcc76eed3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/uckydogie/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Luckydogie <small>(uckydogie)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 25, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have a pro license and I use it on 3 of my websites. I created a page on the main website and exported to the other, but having trouble to adapt the content to the new site. So I created a test page (www.mysite.com/test-page) to import the template, because I didn\'t want to leave the broken page on my live site. I submitted a ticket, a rep responded to me, and said \"I don\'t see you have pro license on that site. I only see you have license on www.mysite.com. I told him the link I shared was only a test page, but it\'s under the domain, elementor doesn\'t require license on every page. So I shared screenshots of my license page, my account on Elementor website, to get support. How can they hire such a stupid people for customer support?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Terrible Performance  Slowed Down My Entire Site</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zannatunnime2018/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/debe685844c1f7c31779f6212aeb1f04ddfdbf6856359c4d8f62c25ac779aa04?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/debe685844c1f7c31779f6212aeb1f04ddfdbf6856359c4d8f62c25ac779aa04?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zannatunnime2018/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">zannatunnime2018</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 21, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It completely ruined my sites speed. Pages took forever to load, and overall performance dropped badly after installing it. No matter how much I optimized, the loading time stayed slow. If speed and smooth performance matter to you, Id stay away from Elementor. Very disappointed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesome Page builder</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bennedict/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9ffc61f15f1be38e6b54ca0102bc8e04e8926705d1e97ba7bc89864207da8e41?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9ffc61f15f1be38e6b54ca0102bc8e04e8926705d1e97ba7bc89864207da8e41?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bennedict/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">bennedict</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 19, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I\'ve been using Elementor for over 4 years now, it\'s the best page builder on WordPress. I love it!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:145:\"The Elementor Website Builder has it all: drag and drop page builder, pixel perfect design, mobile responsive editing, and more. Get started now!\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:59:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.3.28.4.zip\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:0:{}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:6:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-1.gif?rev=3005087\";s:7:\"caption\";s:144:\"<strong>Visual Drag and Drop Editor</strong> - Design your website layouts and place any element anywhere on the page for pixel-perfect designs.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-2.gif?rev=3005087\";s:7:\"caption\";s:185:\"<strong>Full Design System</strong> - Enjoy a professional workflow and ensure consistency across your site. Define your settings, use them globally, and instantly adjust them any time.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-3.gif?rev=3005087\";s:7:\"caption\";s:170:\"<strong>Responsive Design</strong> Fully edit your website and customize the behavior on desktop, tablet, &amp; mobile to optimi